message: Hi Bob, I'm offering you this great product for $95. Let me know if you're interested!
Hi Alice, thanks for the offer. I appreciate the product and I'm ready to buy if you can offer it for $85.
Hi Bob, thanks for your counteroffer. I'm not able to go as low as $85, but I can offer the product for $90. Let me know what you think!
Hi Bob, I understand your position. How about we settle at $90? It's a good deal for both of us.
